questions.question: Given data X = 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10 and 11 and respective values of Y for all X values are 2.718, 3.320, 4.055, 4.953, 6.050, 7.389 and 9.025. Find the value of Integration of Y with Trapezoidal rule.
Given data X = 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7 and 8 and respective values of Y for all X values are 1.492, 1.822, 2.225, 2.718, 3.320, 4.055, 4.953. Find the value of Integration of Y with Trapezoidal rule.
